00:14:47.740 --> 00:14:49.180 align:middle line:84%
I would imagine
what it would feel

00:14:49.180 --> 00:14:52.090 align:middle line:90%
like never have to go back.

00:14:52.090 --> 00:14:56.390 align:middle line:84%
The still cigarettes
and still alcohol

00:14:56.390 --> 00:15:00.840 align:middle line:84%
and being afraid all the
time, I wanted to stay there

00:15:00.840 --> 00:15:02.550 align:middle line:90%
with my grandparents.

00:15:02.550 --> 00:15:05.430 align:middle line:90%
I could never figure out a way.

00:15:05.430 --> 00:15:08.100 align:middle line:84%
The time always came where
we had to get in the car

00:15:08.100 --> 00:15:10.800 align:middle line:90%
and go back.

00:15:10.800 --> 00:15:15.300 align:middle line:84%
My grandmother one day asked me
to walk down to the mailboxes

00:15:15.300 --> 00:15:17.010 align:middle line:90%
to get the mail for her.

00:15:17.010 --> 00:15:20.020 align:middle line:84%
I think she had two
pieces of mail that day.

00:15:20.020 --> 00:15:24.090 align:middle line:84%
And I was walking along
the railroad tracks that

00:15:24.090 --> 00:15:26.550 align:middle line:90%
led to the path to our home.

00:15:26.550 --> 00:15:29.250 align:middle line:84%
And I was walking balancing
on the railroad tracks

00:15:29.250 --> 00:15:32.040 align:middle line:90%
like kids always do.

00:15:32.040 --> 00:15:35.730 align:middle line:84%
There seemed to be kind of
like a shimmer, something

00:15:35.730 --> 00:15:38.610 align:middle line:84%
like in the air
changed in front of me.

00:15:38.610 --> 00:15:42.090 align:middle line:84%
And a woman, and she
looked quite old,

00:15:42.090 --> 00:15:44.340 align:middle line:90%
she must have been in her 30s.

00:15:44.340 --> 00:15:47.310 align:middle line:90%
I was 12, so she looked old.

00:15:47.310 --> 00:15:50.430 align:middle line:84%
She looked familiar
somehow and she told me,

00:15:50.430 --> 00:15:54.240 align:middle line:84%
she says, "I am an
older version of you.

00:15:54.240 --> 00:15:57.970 align:middle line:90%
And I am here with a message.

00:15:57.970 --> 00:16:03.500 align:middle line:84%
And that is to let you know
that you are deeply loved.

00:16:03.500 --> 00:16:07.400 align:middle line:84%
And that you will make
it through adulthood.

00:16:07.400 --> 00:16:11.120 align:middle line:84%
You will live," because that
was my fear that I would not

00:16:11.120 --> 00:16:13.820 align:middle line:90%
live through my childhood.

00:16:13.820 --> 00:16:15.290 align:middle line:84%
I never imagined
what I would look

00:16:15.290 --> 00:16:20.270 align:middle line:84%
like when I became old in my
30s, never entered my mind.

00:16:20.270 --> 00:16:24.860 align:middle line:84%
But I trusted her and carried
that message in my heart.

00:16:24.860 --> 00:16:27.440 align:middle line:84%
I vowed to myself
not to tell anyone

00:16:27.440 --> 00:16:32.270 align:middle line:84%
because people would think I
was a bit loopy, a bit crazy

00:16:32.270 --> 00:16:35.730 align:middle line:84%
to have experienced
something like that.

00:16:35.730 --> 00:16:39.200 align:middle line:90%
And so no one else knew.

00:16:39.200 --> 00:16:42.620 align:middle line:84%
But in times of challenge
throughout my childhood,

00:16:42.620 --> 00:16:46.460 align:middle line:84%
I remembered her message and
it really brought me hope.

00:16:46.460 --> 00:16:51.820 align:middle line:84%
I felt warmth and love
within, with that.

00:16:51.820 --> 00:16:55.446 align:middle line:90%
And that was my first download.

00:16:55.446 --> 00:16:59.500 align:middle line:10%
>> My family was a great
family, unconditionally loving,

00:16:59.500 --> 00:17:01.380 align:middle line:10%
wonderful, but also
really messed up.

00:17:01.380 --> 00:17:06.510 align:middle line:10%
And I had a borderline
abusive, I would say,

00:17:06.510 --> 00:17:09.599 align:middle line:10%
