00:17:21.329 --> 00:17:22.440 align:middle line:90%
there was a rocking chair.

00:17:22.440 --> 00:17:23.730 align:middle line:90%
It was empty usually.

00:17:23.730 --> 00:17:31.170 align:middle line:84%
