what I look like,

00:17:35.730 --> 00:17:38.010 align:middle line:84%
I see that that was
probably myself.

00:17:38.010 --> 00:17:39.550 align:middle line:84%
And she would just
be there with me.

00:17:39.550 --> 00:17:40.675 align:middle line:90%
And she would just be kind.

00:17:40.675 --> 00:17:44.700 align:middle line:84%
