00:17:49.170 --> 00:17:50.280 align:middle line:90%
and you're going to be OK.

00:17:50.280 --> 00:17:51.420 align:middle line:90%
It's all going to turn out OK."

00:17:51.420 --> 00:17:53.712 align:middle line:84%
