00:33:40.695 --> 00:33:43.935 align:middle line:10%
>> So the church issued
an edict and they said--

00:33:43.935 --> 00:33:46.500 align:middle line:10%
>> The religious authorities
will look after the souls

00:33:46.500 --> 00:33:49.500 align:middle line:10%
of everyone, and the natural
philosophers were OK as long

00:33:49.500 --> 00:33:52.035 align:middle line:10%
as they just looked
at the physical world.

00:33:52.035 --> 00:33:57.510 align:middle line:84%
>> You guys in science, you
have things of materiality.

00:33:57.510 --> 00:33:58.950 align:middle line:90%
That's fine.

00:33:58.950 --> 00:34:02.850 align:middle line:84%
Things which involve
spirit, read consciousness,

00:34:02.850 --> 00:34:04.095 align:middle line:90%
that's our bailiwick.

00:34:04.095 --> 00:34:09.270 align:middle line:10%
>> Very sensible because if
