00:34:18.130 --> 00:34:21.280 align:middle line:84%
Or you were burnt at the
stake like Giordano Bruno was.

00:34:21.280 --> 00:34:25.449 align:middle line:84%
>> The Inquisition actually
began in 1232 but it really

00:34:25.449 --> 00:34:28.810 align:middle line:84%
takes force with the
Council of Trent.

00:34:28.810 --> 00:34:31.929 align:middle line:84%
In general, for
most scientists, it

00:34:31.929 --> 00:34:34.840 align:middle line:84%
became a taboo
subject, consciousness.

00:34:34.840 --> 00:34:38.630 align:middle line:84%
It was just not worth the
hassle of getting into.

00:34:38.630 --> 00:34:39.670 align:middle line:90%
And so they didn't.

00:34:39.670 --> 00:34:41.710 align:middle line:90%
>> But it creates a schism.

00:34:41.710 --> 00:34:44.830 align:middle line:84%
And that schism just
grew, and so scientists

00:34:44.830 --> 00:34:48.880 align:middle line:84%
began to denigrate
religion and spirituality.

00:34:48.880 --> 00:34:51.940 align:middle line:84%
And spirituality sort
of kept on its track.

00:34:51.940 --> 00:34:56.274 align:middle line:84%
So the two just separated
literally in their worldviews.

00:34:56.274 --> 00:34:59.890 align:middle line:84%
>> And for almost 300 years,
that's the way things went.

00:34:59.890 --> 00:35:04.690 align:middle line:84%
I mean, the last person killed
