00:35:23.230 --> 00:35:25.660 align:middle line:84%
It brought us all
the technologies

00:35:25.660 --> 00:35:28.240 align:middle line:84%
that make our lives
so much easier today.

00:35:28.240 --> 00:35:33.550 align:middle line:84%
But its basic premise
