00:36:02.170 --> 00:36:03.850 align:middle line:90%
That was the story.

00:36:03.850 --> 00:36:08.050 align:middle line:84%
So it's a story of
separation, of accident,

00:36:08.050 --> 00:36:11.510 align:middle line:84%
of meaninglessness,
