00:37:12.520 --> 00:37:17.350 align:middle line:84%
You see, and that's
really what's

00:37:17.350 --> 00:37:21.670 align:middle line:90%
happened to the human kind.

00:37:21.670 --> 00:37:24.700 align:middle line:10%
>> You take then the theories
that we understand from

00:37:24.700 --> 00:37:26.870 align:middle line:10%
